<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun a chawm taluo ie simlei nunnawpna,
 Pak bang tuoiin sangmuol a liem zel hi;
 Gi bang khenna'n lenkawl ah chung sunni a suok.

[V2]
 Chang bang damin guol ngaihte, Gi bang ki khen tai tiu;
 Lautha puiha I gam leh vangkhuo zuon dingin,
 Lal Isu'n nau bang ei pui hen lamtawn in,
 Chang bang dama dawn bang kituok kit di'n.

[V3]
 2. Hansiedawl sietlei ah nunnawp peh bang kim theilo,
 Gi bang kikhen tai tiu Lal na sem di'n.
 Ginnan Kalvari-ah dawn bang kituok khawm di'n.

[V4]
 3. Sietlei hi guol ngaih chang bang kikhenna himah leh,
 Hai bang I ngak ni lopi hung tung ding,
 Tieng chuleh nau bang kahna nunnawpna suok ding.

[V5]
 4. Gi bang khenlohna ding thimthu la ki lel theilo,
 Hun muol liemsa la sap kit theih hilo,
 Gi bang khenlohna Salem thak mu bang I ngai.</lyrics>
<title>Gibang Kikhen Tai Tiu</title>
<author>Pautinkhup</author>
<hymn_number>283</hymn_number>
</song>